node.text: Throw my wobbly cat a birthday party!!🎉🎉🎉🎉 we love you shakey 💝 #cerebellarhypoplasia #cat #wobblycat #specialneeds #birthday
Protect the wobbly kitty at all costs. ❤️
Happy Birthday You Beautiful Fur Baby! May your day be filled with love and happiness 🎉🥳🤗😻
Happy Birthday Shakey! You are a shining star. ✨🤩😍🎂🎉🥳❤️
@diary.annee_ yo, add me, I need to join the party
@zotaeha the glitter will get in his fur and get in his mouth 🚫
@omni.scienttt maybe you want your cat to become blind on his birthday but not everyone
The glitter bomb was unnecessary for my cute poor cat☝🏻😔
Happy Late Birthday Shakey, you adorable cat 💚
the only bday party i would attend if invited 🥳🎂🎉
@nai.cpds_ I think in spanish it would be hipoplasia cerebral...
@dasramy No, it's called ataxia. It's a disease of the cerebellum, which coordinates space/movement, speech, coordination, etc. Search "cat ataxia" on YouTube.
@fucking.alvarito no it is not 😉 you can double check in the account that posted the vid that in this case it is CH ...
At some point it's making me feel sad
EU QUERO UM GATO ASSIM, QUE ANDE EXATAMENTE ASSIM
